    "data": [
        [
            [
                ""
            ],
            [
                "I looked at Helpie with ‘save me’ eyes"
            ],
            [
                "but to my surprise, Helpie was already on their way to grab “Johhney#6769”."
            ],
            [
                "HUH??? LET ME GO YOU CLANKER. YOU’RE RUINING MY CHANCES TO GET LAID."
            ],
            [
                "Helpie drags the man away and gets them kicked out of the cafeteria."
            ],
            [
                "What a start."
            ],
            [
                "I exhale after all that ruckus and finally relax."
            ],
            [
                " As soon as I got up to thank Helpie, I hear a bell across the cafeteria."
            ],
            [
                "One of the organizers yells:"
            ],
            [
                "“Every time you hear this bell, that means you have a minute to switch places.”"
            ],
            [
                "And soon after, a very unique person sits on my table."
            ],
            [
                "Damn… what a weirdo, eh? Are you okay?"
            ],
            [
                "Yes… Peace comes after the storm"
            ],
            [
                "and this was definitely my reward after enduring such bullshit."
            ],
            [
                "The beautiful person’s nametag says ‘[Victor]’ in pretty handwriting."
            ],
            [
                "U-uh… yeah, I’m fine… this isn’t the first weirdo I've encountered in my life…"
            ],
            [
                "unfortunately."
            ],
            [
                "Tell me about it!"
            ],
            [
                "Heads up, if the girl over there with the striped shirt sits with you,"
            ],
            [
                "be prepared to hear about how much she hates your looks for at least 20 minutes."
            ],
            [
                "Why are people like those here if they aren’t even gonna be nice? Haha!"
            ],
            [
                "We both chuckle."
            ],
            [
                "So… [Victor]. I see you’ve got piercings, how many do you have?"
            ],
            [
                "As of right now, I’ve got like 9."
            ],
            [
                "That’s weird… [he] doesn’t seem to have that many on [his] face."
            ],
            [
                "What? But I can only count 5 on your face, where are the others?"
            ],
            [
                "[Victor] blushes at the direct question, but smirks with confidence as they lean back on the seat."
            ],
            [
                "You’re a bold one. I’d be wrong to say that I don’t like that."
            ],
            [
                "[Victor] smirks at me as I still don’t know how my question was bold, so I just scratch my head and keep on smiling."
            ],
            [
                "I guess, haha. So…could you tell me about yourself?"
            ],
            [
                "Well [tn], answering your question, I am a very simple human"
            ],
            [
                "I enjoy taking care of my plants, collecting vinyls..."
            ],
            [
                "and I’ve got a passion for mixology."
            ],
            [
                "Actually, I’m a barista at the Aukademi uni café"
            ],
            [
                "So, [tn], will free drinks and pastries be enough to convince you to accept me?"
            ],
            [
                "[Victor] winks as [he] leans on the table to tell me [his] last killer phrase."
            ],
            [
                "Honestly, [his] smile and confidence could melt anyone very easily."
            ],
            [
                "I even felt shivers down my spine. "
            ],
            [
                "No way… I study at Aukademi! I’ll come and say hi sometime."
            ],
            [
                "And maybe check if drinks are really your thing."
            ],
            [
                "Cool, cool… Something tells me you’ll be there very often."
            ],
            [
                "Before I could say anything else, We hear the bell and [Victor] stands up while looking at me."
            ],
            [
                "[He] then approaches me and begins writing [his] phone on the back of my hand. "
            ],
            [
                "[tn], talking to you was quite nice. I think we’ve got hella chemistry"
            ],
            [
                "So I better not see you talking to that striped shirt girl, eh?"
            ],
            [
                "[Victor] then raises [his] eyebrows at [his] joke and we both laugh."
            ],
            [
                " I was feeling bad when all that Johhney thing happened"
            ],
            [
                "but after speaking with [Victor], the air even felt cleaner,"
            ],
            [
                "with a faint citric smell."
            ],
            [
                "Is Victor a green or red flag?"
            ]
        ],
